{
  "stem": "734.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was the Lublin-oriented government, which was the left, OK?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That all, I knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But as to who was doing what, who they were, how many people?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You never got such information.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The fact is, less you knew, the better off you were.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In that sense, the better off everybody else was in case of a downfall, in case of arrest or something.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you knew a lot, chances are, under torture, you started to leak information.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That happened, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And once you leak information, then everybody goes, right?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The less you know, safer it is for the movement.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this was the policy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just knew Alexandra, Joanna, and her brother, Lech.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was it-- and [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Victor, ?] later on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Victor, ?] who, when I already worked at the other studio, in '42, '43, and one day [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Victor ?] come-- come comes along to tell me that he needs two photos of mine for a-- for a forged ID card.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he says, my name is [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Victor. ?] [LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he came to tell me that I shouldn't worry about Alexandra, she's OK.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that his name is [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Victor. ?] And he needs two photos.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The following day, he came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I gave him the two photos.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And two days later, he came back with the ID, with a-- with my forged ID card.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Branislav ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Gotlewski, ?] the initials didn't change, B-- BG.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He-- he-- he said to me, I'll see to it that you'll-- you'll-- you keep-- you'll keep the same initials.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was the only time I saw him.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
